# Parquet / Large Data Files
# Ignored by default, EXCEPT the two files the backend actually loads at
# runtime (clustered.parquet, hotspot_scores_v2.parquet) - those are kept
# so the app works out of the box after a fresh clone.
*.parquet
!clustered.parquet
!hotspot_scores_v2.parquet

